    "description": "Hungry Critters are coming for your carrots, can you shoo them away in this casual yet strategic Tower Defense game?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEND THE GARDEN</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/856c7059f0d2209aae2f15673ca2e279.poster.avif?t=1682633449\" width=674 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/856c7059f0d2209aae2f15673ca2e279.webm?t=1682633449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/856c7059f0d2209aae2f15673ca2e279.mp4?t=1682633449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play on <strong>4 difficulties</strong> and earn <strong>over 20 Steam Achievements</strong>.<br>Earn <strong>7 permanent upgrades</strong> through the Boneyard, by <strong>completing maps to earn Bones</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INFUSE THE DOGGOS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/3e368fc835a35332887e6a90da2bd977.poster.avif?t=1682633449\" width=675 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/3e368fc835a35332887e6a90da2bd977.webm?t=1682633449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Upgrade your Doggos</strong> beyond their natural limits by stuffing them full of Kibble!<br>We don't recommend this in real life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE THE SEASONS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/f1fa8690dbc27b3a6e33864a5eb31943.poster.avif?t=1682633449\" width=674 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/f1fa8690dbc27b3a6e33864a5eb31943.webm?t=1682633449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/f1fa8690dbc27b3a6e33864a5eb31943.mp4?t=1682633449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Complete <strong>8 unique maps</strong>, themed after the four seasons.<br>Some maps offer more space than others, will you <strong>recruit many Doggos</strong>, or will you <strong>infuse a select few</strong>?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHOO AWAY THE... GATLING SNAIL?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/687b8084297bbc1bc406b05a18b70392.poster.avif?t=1682633449\" width=674 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/687b8084297bbc1bc406b05a18b70392.webm?t=1682633449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368390/extras/687b8084297bbc1bc406b05a18b70392.mp4?t=1682633449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Who gave this guy gatling guns <i>AND </i>cool shades? That wasn't in the budget! We don't have a budget!!!<br>Venture through<strong> Hecc difficulty</strong> to shoo away the elusive Snailord.<br>He'll be fine, we promise. <i>Very cool shades</i> offer great protection from Doggos.",
